title: Secret Craft, Hidden Photos - Lieutenant Bob Walker / Disclosure Project Witness Testimony Archive
description: See more at http://www.SiriusDisclosure.com. Lieutenant Bob Walker was a 2nd lieutenant in the Army. After World War II at a NASA (then NACA) open house, he saw a 30-foot saucer-shaped craft which had been brought back from Germany for study. On another occasion, he was piloting an aircraft for a TV station when a disc shaped object came in from the west. He had his camera and climbed to 12,000 feet to take some photos of it.
